StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetCi.es]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
( @Code varchar(4) = '0000', @StateCode varchar(2), @CountyCode varchar(3) = '000' ) AS
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT c.[ID], c.[Code], c.[Name], c.[CountyCode], c.[CountyName], c.[StateName] FROM [USMC].[vwCi.es] c WHERE (c.StateCode = @StateCode AND @Code = '0000' AND @CountyCode = '000') OR (c.StateCode = @StateCode AND @Code = '0000' AND c.CountyCode = @CountyCode) OR (c.StateCode = @StateCode AND c.Code = @Code AND @CountyCode = '000')
